title: Meditation
smallDescription: Learn to meditate in just a few minutes a day.
longDescription: Start a journey of self-discovery with this beginner-friendly mindfulness challenge. In just 30 days, learn to become a calm, level-headed person with simple daily tasks starting with just 5 minutes meditation.
